        <heading>2498.  Prescription of actions for supplement or diminution of price or for dissolution</heading>
        <content>
          <p>Art. 2498.  Prescription of actions for supplement or diminution of price or for dissolution
The seller's action for an increase of the price and the buyer's actions for diminution of the price or dissolution of the sale for shortage or excessive surplus in the extent of the immovable sold prescribe one year from the day of the sale.</p>
        </content>
